Class ReplenishmentRequest

java.lang.Object
com.group6.hms.app.managers.inventory.models.ReplenishmentRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ReplenishmentRequest extends Object implements Serializable
The ReplenishmentRequest class represents a request to replenish a specific amount of medication stock. It includes details such as the request ID, medication, quantity to replenish, and the current status of the request. This class implements Serializable to allow for storage and retrieval.
